# Portfolio Website — Implementation Plan

## Goal

Build a premium, animation-rich portfolio website inspired by [prototypestudio.fr](https://www.prototypestudio.fr/), using the user's provided design system (colors, fonts, references). The site must feel luxurious, smooth, and highly polished — matching the reference's quality of scroll animations, hover states, and pacing.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Purpose |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| Framework | **Next.js 15** (App Router) | SSR, routing, scalability |
| Styling | **Tailwind CSS v4** | Utility-first CSS with custom design tokens |
| Animation | **GSAP 3** + **ScrollTrigger** | Scroll-driven and timeline animations |
| Smooth Scroll | **Lenis** | Premium buttery-smooth scrolling |
| Fonts | **Custom** (DeanGothic, Silvana) + **Google Fonts** (Epilogue, Manrope, Space Grotesk) | Typography system |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> You specified Tailwind CSS — I'll use **Tailwind CSS v4** (the latest). Please confirm if you'd prefer v3 instead.

---

