## Verification Plan

### Automated
- `npm run build` — Ensure clean production build with no errors
- `npm run dev` — Verify hot reload and dev server
- Lighthouse audit for performance score (target: 90+)

### Browser Testing
- Visual comparison against reference screenshots
- Scroll animation smoothness verification
- Responsive testing (mobile, tablet, desktop)
- Hover state and interaction testing

### Manual
- Request user review of the live dev server
- Compare against the provided video reference for animation pacing
